  m_text: "You have beat the demo of break free, I hope you enjoyed and \nexplored
    all the rooms. I put a lot of effort into making it a fun\nand challenging experience.\n\nI
    would also like to give a massive thanks to my friend josh york \nfor doing the
    sound design for my project.\n\nFeel free to play the game again, by pressing
    the button on the \nright or if you want to \"break free\" press the button on
    the left\n"
